        "text_zUHpG8": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><br/>【The IGOGOMI Fold】All the benefits of an E-bike has packed into the original 3-part fold. It takes around 25-seconds to transform your bike into a small compact package (26 ×  13  × 28.7 inches )（L × W × H）,that you can tow, stow and carry anywhere. Travels on rush-hour trains, metros, underground, overground, car trunks, and cabs. There is no need to leave it outside. Just enjoy the ride<br/></li><li><br/>【Your ride, You decide】 Customize your ride performance with 3 riding modes. Go full throttle up to 19 mile/h on battery power alone. But the IGOGOMI folding bike also rides like a traditional pedal-only bicycle. Need some extra oomph? Turn on the pedal-to-go for a boost of electric power as you pedal. It simplifies the riding experience for you.<br/></li><li><br/>【Charge on the go】The compact IGOGOMI Electric 36V / 6.8Ah lithium-ion battery packs in the power. The range is 25-35miles. Charging it is just as simple as plugging in your phone. Plug into any standard outlet and fully charge in 4 hours. <br/></li><li><br/>【The IGOGOMI Fold】All the benefits of an E-bike has packed into the original 3-part fold. It takes around 25-seconds to transform your bike into a small compact package (26 ×  13  × 28.7 inches )（L × W × H）,that you can tow, stow and carry anywhere. Travels on rush-hour trains, metros, underground, overground, car trunks, and cabs. There is no need to leave it outside. Just enjoy the ride<br/></li><li><br/>【Your ride, You decide】 Customize your ride performance with 3 riding modes. Go full throttle up to 19 mile/h on battery power alone. But the IGOGOMI folding bike also rides like a traditional pedal-only bicycle. Need some extra oomph? Turn on the pedal-to-go for a boost of electric power as you pedal. It simplifies the riding experience for you.<br/></li><li><br/>【Charge on the go】The compact IGOGOMI Electric 36V / 6.8Ah lithium-ion battery packs in the power. The range is 25-35miles. Charging it is just as simple as plugging in your phone. Plug into any standard outlet and fully charge in 4 hours. <br/></li></ul><p></p>"
          }
        },
